# Dotfiles Project Standards

When working in this dotfiles repository:

- Follow platform-specific conventions (Linux, macOS, Server, Anonymous)
- Maintain backward compatibility when possible
- Document changes in comments and commit messages
- Test changes before committing when possible
- Keep secrets secured using git-secret
- Organize files logically by function and platform
- Use symlinks for files, create directories when needed

Remember that this project supports multiple platforms:
- Linux (general)
- macOS
- Server (minimalist setup)
- Anonymous (privacy-focused setup)
